          <p>Hostinger is one of the world's most popular web hosting companies, serving over 3 million customers across 150+ countries. Founded in 2004, they've built a reputation for offering reliable hosting at prices that are hard to beat — especially for beginners.</p>
          <p>I've personally used Hostinger for my own website (<a href="https://irecommendu.com">irecommendu.com</a>), so this review comes from real experience, not just research.</p>

          <h2>Pricing</h2>
          <p>Hostinger's pricing is genuinely one of its biggest strengths. Here's what you can expect:</p>

          <div class="pricing-table">
